{"tid":128264,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件想幫人，但變左害人嘅事","createTime":"2017-02-20T16:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T17:03:59.000Z","uid":34580,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26c345b0a3673676dc5a29b054f70a403ac2bfcd","tid":128264,"uid":34580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:14:55.000Z","msg":"搭巴士坐下層最後<br />\n落車前見到隔離個啊婆訓緊教<br />\n有袋橙喺地下（佢本身將所有野放喺隔離位）<br />\n多手幫佢執起，點知個袋穿窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目測有7至8個橙，有幾個仲要沿住保齡球位碌<br />\n我就一路避住啲橙，一路急急腳落車<br />\n途中好似唔小心一腳踢左個橙去車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後頭也不回落車<br />\n唔知個啊婆執左幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1503a185ecd446bb3cf59e895735a31c394c5f","tid":128264,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"老豆老母想生個叻仔<br />\n點知生咗我"},{"pid":"19926f7e7346f9242a46ebca0b7fe21074296fe9","tid":128264,"uid":34580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆老母想生個叻仔<br />\n點知生咗我</blockquote><br />\n咁我係你就跳樓死左佢"},{"pid":"4445b94e9336f71e4ba6f3ffe84233fac3c19dd3","tid":128264,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆老母想生個叻仔<br />\n點知生咗我</blockquote><br />\n咁我係你就跳樓死左佢</blockquote><br />\n教唆他人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112cd0b588b83f048daac58ef549b1fabd8179f1","tid":128264,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆老母想生個叻仔<br />\n點知生咗我</blockquote><br />\n咁我係你就跳樓死左佢</blockquote><br />\n樓主你真貼題"},{"pid":"120559c8fbc95ae7cbb28ea80857b16618cf6312","tid":128264,"uid":34580,"like":0,"dislike":